name: Diamante Metal Guitar Long Silver Necklace
description:
Metal diamante effect guitar charm necklace
The silver coloured chain measures 30 inches long with a 3 inch extension chain

	The colour on the guitar may vary depending on the light, from light grey to dark grey

	The charm measures approx 9cm long, 2.8cm wide

	Perfect for the kitsch, emo or scene look!
